# 8. Project Demonstration (ProjectDemonstration.pdf)

# Project Demonstration

## Project Title

A Comprehensive Measure of Well-Being using Machine Learning

---

## Demonstration Overview

The demonstration presents the complete workflow of the project, beginning with data collection and preprocessing, followed by model training, evaluation, and deployment through a Flask web application.

---

## Demonstration Steps

### Step 1

Launch the Flask application.

---

### Step 2

Open the application in a web browser.

---

### Step 3

Enter the following values:

* Life Expectancy
* Mean Years of Schooling
* Gross National Income Per Capita

---

### Step 4

Click **Predict HDI**.

---

### Step 5

The application processes the input using the trained Linear Regression model and displays the predicted Human Development Index.

---

