## Future Enhancements

* Add multiple machine learning algorithms.
* Improve prediction accuracy with advanced models.
* Deploy the application on a cloud platform.
* Integrate interactive dashboards and visual analytics.
* Enable user authentication and data history.

---

## Conclusion

The project demonstrates an end-to-end machine learning solution for predicting the Human Development Index. It combines data preprocessing, model development, evaluation, and Flask deployment into a practical and user-friendly application suitable for educational and research purposes.
